Package: RCGLS
Type: Package
Title: Download data provided by the Copernicus Global Land Service and open this data in R.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Willemijn Vroege
Maintainer: Willemijn Vroege <wvroege@ethz.ch>
Description: These functions rely on the data provided in the data manifest of the Copernicus service.
These functinos allow to download data from the Copernicus Global Land Service Manifest. But you need to register at https://land.copernicus.eu/global/ and create a username and password.
Imports: RCurl, ncdf4, raster
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
